    Certification

    public static enum Certification.Phase
extends java.lang.Enum<Certification.Phase>
    An enumeration of Phases or States that a certification can be in.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      Active
      Decisions are actively being made on a certification.
      Challenge
      The certification is in a state where decisions can be challenged, for example, a user can challenge a remediation request claiming that they still need the access that is to be removed.
      End
      A final phase to transition to after all other phases are complete.
      Remediation
      The certification remediation requests have been sent and the identities are periodically refreshed to see if the requested remediations have occurred.
      Staged
      The certification has been generated, but is not active in the system.
